Mura Converter
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INTRODUCTION
This converter is designed to take data from another CMS and import it into a new Mura site

CURRENTLY SUPPORTED IMPORT FORMATS
Wordpress XML


WHAT'S NEW

Feb 23/2013

- Added selector to import comments or not
- Merged in devel branch features for importing comments (not tested or made visible yet while testing), this should be enough to merge this out.

Feb 22/2013

- Added support for importing WP pubdate into Mura Content Release Dates
- Added selecting a location in Mura under which to import Wordpress blog posts
- Added migration of Wordpress friendly SEO url to Mura's SEO title
- Added migration of Wordpress Author to Mura Credits field
- Added migration of setting published posts as visible in mura, and leaving drafts as hidden and out of Mura Navigation
- Updated Wordpress screen with detailed instructions for Mura Administrators

